result.name: Honorary Family

reviews.text: Nice place to go for dinner. However, it is quite expensive for tea time. Four hundred something for six persons for a morning tea.
Nice local place good food

When asked where to find good dim sim in Hong Kong, locals will tell you.... 'The place downstairs!' That is how good the standards are throughout the city and it is the case with the Honorary Family restaurant in Fo Tan, located in the small shopping centre next to the Royal Ascot Residential complex. Opening hours are 7.30am to 9.30pm daily. 

This is a large restaurant with plenty of seating. You'll find it quite full throughout the day, a good sign when looking for a place to have dim sum. I eat here from time to time including a recent meal with a colleague of mine. We ordered fried spring rolls with prawn, prawn dumpling, steamed bbq pork buns and rice rolls with bbq pork along with a pot of Jasmine tea. Everything tasted good as expected. Meal cost was HK$140 for two people, a reasonably price for four dim sum baskets.

Note: To place your dim sum order, you will be given a three fold card with a long list of dim sum orders in both Cantonese and English. Just tick the circle next to your choices and hand your card to a server. Your dim sum will then be brought out as various baskets are ready. Eat them as soon as they are served, don't wait for remaining orders, they will come when they are available. Lastly, I recommend ordering 3 baskets for every 2 people, have an extra basket if you're hungrier than usual. 

In the end, Honorary Family is a good place for dim sum. In any other city in the world, you'd call this very good dim sum. In Hong Kong, its just one of many, many places that serve up good dim sum.
The price is reasonable and the food is ok. However, the location is inconvenient
nice food for group lunch and dinner

reviews.text: 腸粉好吃，但是點了一道香煎薄脆餅，結果送來的感覺根本是個香煎厚軟捲.....有點被名字騙了的感覺，太失望了拍照都忘了拍....裡面的椰蓉跟砂糖甜的不行，吃的好膩，又煎的很油，還又厚又軟，真的太失望了，吃了幾口就不想吃了
午膳不錯,容易有位,但如泊單必需12點前到,否則要輪候。

result.name: 裕滿人家

reviews.text: 食物水準穩定，食材屬中上水平， 以貨論價，價錢合理。地方舒適清潔。晚飯時段除非是特別日子否則通常容易找到位。只是食店員工招呼只是一般。 最有問題是每晚奉六點半，食店老闆都會裝香，弄到大半間酒樓都有燒香的味道， 大大影響食慾。
人不多，可以慢慢坐下傾下計。片皮鴨同冬瓜盅都好好食。
飲茶午飯這兒算是比較安靜（對比其他嘈吵的茶樓），坐位空間充分，食物可以。
叫咗點心個幾鐘都未到
火炭分店的點心非常好，又夠熱又美味！唯獨是未能試到……灌湯餃！
